title: About
text:
Stacks on Stacks is a microblog maintained by RDS @ Utrecht University Library
The name Stacks on Stacks refers to the structured information and physical composition of the library.
Information on library activies, events, and goings on, will be posted here with some frequency.
You can interact with these posts via Hypothes.is
